  "_hardening_doc": "90574654: runtime-recovery hardening knobs (DISTINCT from bmad_hardening). silent_death_respawn_cap is the ONE shared respawn budget across both silent-death sub-classes (log_empty/log_truncated), persisted via state.recovery_attempts so it survives relaunch/--resume; 0 disables respawn; absent/malformed falls back to compiled default 1.",
